📌PROTESTKARTE: GEMEINSAM FÜR DIE ZUKUNFT

In kaum einem anderen Bundesland schießen Containerdörfer schneller aus dem Boden, als im widerständigen Sachsen.

Jahrelang zerfielen von Plauen bis Zittau Grundschulen, wurde Infrastruktur zurückgebaut, Supermärkte und Arztpraxen geschlossen. Was an erhaltenden Grundmaßnahmen des Staates für die deutsche Bevölkerung unzumutbar war, wird für Migranten blitzmobilisiert.

Wir sind in der Dauerkrise. Aber in Sachsen und ganz Ostdeutschland regen sich die 🥁Proteste gegen eine korrupte Politik fremder Interessen.

Wir brauchen eine Vision einer neuen Zukunft.

Die Protestkarte liefert die schönen 📽️Bilder des Widerstands – denn niemand ist alleine!👌🏻

📌PROTESTKARTE: GEMEINSAM FÜR DIE ZUKUNFT

In kaum einem anderen Bundesland schießen Containerdörfer schneller aus dem Boden, als im widerständigen Sachsen.

Jahrelang zerfielen von Plauen bis Zittau Grundschulen, wurde Infrastruktur zurückgebaut, Supermärkte und Arztpraxen geschlossen. Was an erhaltenden Grundmaßnahmen des Staates für die deutsche Bevölkerung unzumutbar war, wird für Migranten blitzmobilisiert.

Wir sind in der Dauerkrise. Aber in Sachsen und ganz Ostdeutschland regen sich die 🥁Proteste gegen eine korrupte Politik fremder Interessen.

Wir brauchen eine Vision einer neuen Zukunft.

Die Protestkarte liefert die schönen 📽️Bilder des Widerstands – denn niemand ist alleine!👌🏻

Per supportare il canale e il mio Substack
Ogni tanto qualcuno mi contatta privatamente per chiedere se esiste  qualche modo per supportarmi e quindi supportare il lavoro che faccio qui sul canale e sul mio Substack con articoli di approfondimento.
Premettendo che tutto ciò che scrivo sulle mie piattaforme, attuali e future è, e rimarrà sempre completamente gratuito per tutti, ho deciso di dare la possibilità a chiunque lo desideri, di supportarmi con un aiuto pratico tangibile, ripeto, assolutamente volontario, a partire da due dollari in su, come una tantum o sottoforma di contributo mensile.

The RV park we've been living in has been massively damaged by the current storm washing away Southern California. Overnight our park lost 2 rows of trailers to the river you now see here. 
We were JUST hanging out down by the river last weekend when it was a mere creek...
Meanwhile our RV sustained water damage from flooding last night on top of the most recent storms we've already had here. Since last August we've been living in a 26ft pop-out travel trailer. It is not, I REPEAT NOT EQUIPPED TO HANDLE TORRENTIAL RAINS/WEATHER OF THIS MAGNITUDE. 
Please see my story & highlight reel tilted "RV LIFE" I will add photos & videos there of our current ⚠️EMERGENCY⚠️ situation here. 
I'll be adding a temporary link to my bio for anyone who feels able to donate anything to us so we can relocate asap. 
We need a generator MOST URGENTLY!!! 
We really could use a more appropriately suited RV that can at least keep us all dry! 
And we will likely need to relocate our RV to a new park as well...

I love what I do here online & I pray I've helped  us all gain some knowledge into their evil plans against us all.

Patrons can choose from the 5 tiers to donate options:
10$/25$/75$/150$/500$ Options tier details listed on ATKN Patreon page. Patrons also have the option to just input the exact amount you want to give without a monthly donation plan.

*We accept Equipment! 

ATKN is in need of equipment to help the projects and networks in one way or another so we have updated a list that if you wish you could purchase equipment for us by clicking on the link: https://newegg.io/9452c1a - This link and list will chance frequently also this is not a full list but partial, as new tech comes out or software this list will be updated and replaced.

Jerin Bynum
PO Box 1948
Conway, Ar 72033

*Package Shipping Address:

Jerin Bynum
1111 Main St Ste 1948
Conway, Ar 72032-5410



Where does my money go when donating? 

The first place it goes is to pay for the rumble service, the second equipment immediately needed, the third is to fill the needs of the Ekklesia, those widowed or orphaned  are who we focused on, when we can provide and fill the need we do. Lastly the donations given in good faith are spent only on food and bills for the facility where the network is broadcasted or stationed at the time. Overtime the station will change, God willing.

Will I receive a receipt or tax kick back? 

No, ATKN is not a 501c3 or any entity. Freely we give, freely we receive. We do not sell you the Truth here, donations are as led by the spirit and between you and God.

Some of you may have heard that our friend Jeff Brain, Founder and CEO of Clouthub suffered a stroke right before Christmas. 

Jeff is mentally OK but the left side of his body is experiencing some difficulty and there will be a recovery time. Working on getting him into the bio scaler system to speed that up. 

In the meantime, we are looking to raise $300,000 to continue immediate operations at Clouthub. I’m going to drop the link here if you’d like to donate. I have of course donated and am helping raise some operational capital to keep things moving while he’s recovering. 

On Jeff’s behalf, I want to thank any and all who donate for this amazing platform moving forward. 


Clouthub donation site. If you donate to let them know you’re doing on behalf of Patriot Streetfighter.

content:
Maak de kerst van een dappere vrijheidsstrijder een beetje vrolijker door hem de verlichting te sturen die hij nodig heeft.

Na het redden van de levens van bijna 2.000 Covid-patiënten, waarvan velen in ziekenhuizen adequate medicatie werd geweigerd, kan arts-assistent Scott Miller uit Washington in de nabije toekomst geen legale geneeskunde meer bedrijven.

Miller en vele medische deskundigen beweren dat Covid-patiënten in ziekenhuizen niet echt sterven aan het virus, maar in wezen gegijzeld worden zodra ze zijn opgenomen - bezoek of thuiskomst is verboden - en meestal Remdesivir toegediend krijgen en geïntubeerd worden tot de dood erop volgt.

Als zodanig zijn hij en zijn familie gedegradeerd tot een leven in een tent - en kunnen deze kerst wel wat donaties gebruiken.

Lees hier meer over Scott's verhaal: https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2022/01/physician-assistant-saves-hundreds-covid-patients-needlessly-dying-hospitals-reveals-exactly-medical-license-suspended/

En als je iets over hebt, stuur hem dan wat geld via Venmo: https://venmo.com/code?user_id=3093893893586944640&created=1657565646

Of via GiveSendGo: https://www.givesendgo.com/G3C1F

content:
Make a Brave Freedom Fighter's Christmas a Bit More Merry By Sending Him the Relief He Needs

After saving the lives of nearly 2,000 Covid patients, many of who were refused adequate medications in hospitals, Washington-based Physician Assistant Scott Miller is unable to legally practice medicine for the foreseeable future.

Miller and numerous medical experts contend hospitalized Covid patients are not actually dying from the virus but are essentially held hostage once admitted – prohibited visitation or going home—and are typically administered Remdesivir and intubated to death.

As such, he and his family have been degraded to living in a tent — and could use a few donations this Christmas.

Read more about Scott's story here: https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2022/01/physician-assistant-saves-hundreds-covid-patients-needlessly-dying-hospitals-reveals-exactly-medical-license-suspended/

And if you have a few bucks to spare, please send him some money via Venmo: https://venmo.com/code?user_id=3093893893586944640&created=1657565646

Or via GiveSendGo: https://www.givesendgo.com/G3C1F

content:
Parce que nous ne devons pas oublier le mal qui a été fait à nos enfants et à nous adultes, nous vous proposons de visionner le documentaire "RETROUVONS NOUS" de Patricia ETTOUATI et Philippe GRAU (en trois parties) réalisé à partir de témoignages dont celui de GABIN que nous vous partageons aujourd'hui. Vous découvrirez aussi le témoignage de ROXANE ( maman louve),DIDIER MAÏSTO et des dizaines d'autres personnes.
Ce documentaire sert la mémoire alors foncez le regarder grâce aux liens ci-dessous 
RETROUVONS NOUS partie 1 
Entre Ombres et Lumières
https://peertube.tweb.tv/w/t1aAm17wKULZKNzKtyyAXJ
RETROUVONS NOUS partie 2
Les Violences 
https://peertube.tweb.tv/w/nCH6Km7QETBQV2ZP5PYgoe
RETROUVONS NOUS partie 3
Bâtissons Notre Monde 
https://peertube.tweb.tv/w/iodTRRWYcuMDewp2Le5SNc
Vous pouvez également les aider grâce à cette cagnotte, nous vous rappelons que ce documentaire a été fait de façon totalement bénévole mais un coup de pouce est toujours le bienvenue 
https://donate.stripe.com/28odUM23h7te8a43cc

content:
“Retrouvons-nous” est un film documentaire en trois parties, d’une durée de 7 heures. Retrouvons-nous a vocation a laisser une trace dans les discours sur cette époque, une mémoire pour le présent et pour le futur. Cette oeuvre, ce document est un bien commun qui est en libre accès. Il remet au centre de ce débat l’humain dans sa liberté de pensée et son intelligence collective.

Première partie diffusée le Dimanche 6 Novembre à 18h suivi d'une intervention en direct de Philippe Grau et Patricia Ettouati qui répondront à vos questions en direct.

Multidiffusion sur les plateformes TWEB et Collectif ACID ainsi que sur des médias partenaires présents sur les réseaux :

Facebook, YouTube, Vk, Twitch, Twitter, Telegram, Odysee, Crowdbunker, Peertube et TWEB.TV >>>>> #retrouvonsnous

Anti-censure : https://peertube.tweb.tv

Ce film est proposé en usage éthique, si vous désirez soutenir les créateurs faites un don au chapeau sur :

https://donate.stripe.com/28odUM23h7te8a43cc

Les travailleurs de Big Tech se préparent à une vague massive de licenciements en hiver

🔹Elon Musk s'apprête à supprimer quelque 3 700 emplois chez Twitter, ce qui représente environ la moitié du personnel de l'entreprise, rapporte Reuters.
https://www.reuters.com/technology/twitter-start-layoffs-friday-morning-internal-email-2022-11-04/

🔹Amazon a annoncé une "pause dans les nouvelles embauches au sein de son personnel", invoquant un "environnement macroéconomique inhabituel".
https://www.aboutamazon.com/news/workplace/a-note-about-hiring-from-beth-galetti

🔹Lyft a déclaré qu'il allait licencier environ 680 employés, soit 13% du personnel, et a blâmé l'inflation et le ralentissement de l'économie.
https://d18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net/CIK-0001759509/b016f875-f495-4cb7-a930-36a432649d35.pdf

🔹Le PDG de Stripe, Patrick Collison, a déclaré que la société de paiement allait licencier 14 % de ses effectifs.
https://stripe.com/fr/newsroom/news/ceo-patrick-colli..

🔹Selon Bloomberg, Apple a interrompu le recrutement pour de nombreux postes en dehors de la R&D.
https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2022-11-03/apple-pauses-hiring-for-roles-outside-research-and-development

🔹Les employés de CNN s'attendent à des licenciements après que le patron du réseau, Chris Licht, a mis en garde contre des changements "troublants" à la lumière de "l'inquiétude généralisée concernant les perspectives économiques mondiales."
https://edition.cnn.com/2022/10/26/media/cnn-employees-reliable-sources/index.html

👉🏽 https://t.me/StoryOfBlackBond

Elle peut, en fait, conserver une "image" de n'importe quelle substance dans son noyau moléculaire. Certains scientifiques ont prouvé que l'eau est également vivante, un phénomène connu sous le nom d'eau structurée. Serait-il vraiment possible que l'eau enregistre en permanence l'histoire de sa relation avec le monde par le biais d'amas moléculaires ? Et si oui, que fait-elle de ces informations ?

This is Brad, brother of my friend who passed away, taking Wes’s three girls to school today.

content:
Hello all,

My friend for life, Wes Burleson, passed away this week. He was a great man, father, and patriot. I attended his funeral today and was honored to eulogize him. 

2.5 years ago, he survived a 30’ fall while doing his roofing job. He broke nearly his entire body and suffered brain bleeding. 

6 months after, his wife unexpectedly died. 

This year, he spent 14 days on a ventilator. 

And now, we have lost Wes. Most notably, his fiancé and Wes’s three young daughters lost him. 

His brother has set up this fund for those girls. You know I don’t ask for personal donations to my own cause, nor do I often ask you to donate to candidates. 

But it would lift much anxiety from the shoulders of the broken hearted in Mississippi if you would prayerfully consider giving to this great family. 

If each of you donated one single dollar, you would move mountains and set the three girls up for success.

2.5 years ago, he survived a 30’ fall while doing his roofing job. He broke nearly his entire body and suffered brain bleeding.

This year, he spent 14 days on a ventilator. 

And now, we have lost Wes. Most notably, his fiancé and Wes’s three young daughters lost him.

But it would lift much anxiety from the shoulders of the broken hearted in Mississippi if you would prayerfully consider giving to this great family. 

If each of you donated one single dollar, you would move mountains and set the three girls up for success.

content:
Someone asked for options to donate to my research efforts. Just so you know, I am 100% funded by you guys. While donations are certainly not compulsory, they are appreciated. I don't want to ever have to put things behind paywalls or anything. So, of course at the end of the day, it is up to you. There are a few options for you, if you ever read or watch something I make that particularly inspires you. 

$5 Monthly Donation - This is just kind of a "set it and forget it" kind of thing where you can sign up for a monthly amount.
https://www.subscribestar.com/somebitchiknow

Then there are also two one-time donation options as well. I don't have a crypto wallet yet, but I know I need to. I was deplatformed from Paypal and Patreon lol... so I just gotta keep figuring it out on the fly. :)

Donate Via Cashapp
https://cash.app/$LisfortheWay

Donate Via Venmo
https://venmo.com/lisfortheway

Again, this is not a requirement and if you are not in the position to send anything at this time, that's totally okay. Whenever I publish things, I typically add the links at the end, so maybe some time in the future. Thank you very much. Knowing you guys read what I make is already such a hugely rewarding thing. Money is obviously something needed to live off of, but it's not even close to the most important thing here.

Anyways. Thanks for reading. Just putting it out there because someone asked. ❤️
